      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver. While the mechanical components have been maintained to ensure it runs well, the exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the trim. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It is a solid, functional car for someone who values utility and performance over a perfect cosmetic appearance.",
