      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very sound, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience with all major systems functioning as expected. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor signs of regular use, such as small paint chips or light interior wear. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of quality and value for its next owner.",
