      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! It has some honest character from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone prioritizing reliable transportation and great value. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to get behind the wheel of a hardworking car at an accessible price!",
