    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolute mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it drives just as perfectly as it looks. If you're looking for a total stunner that's been loved and cared for, this is the one. Shoot me a message and come take it for a spin before someone else grabs it!",
