    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained and preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, glass-like luster, completely free from any swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, and the factory-fresh feel is preserved throughout. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation and climate controls, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. It drives with the precision and tightness of a brand-new vehicle, offering a smooth, responsive experience with absolutely no leaks or mechanical imperfections. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that truly looks and performs as though it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
